OL,3,CHow to see tonight's micromoon' - what
OL,4,Cis it and why is it so small?
OL,6,FOne poetic belief says that anything
OL,7,Fbegun under the Flower Moon - whether
OL,8,Fplanting crops, starting
OL,9,Frelationships, or making plans - has
OL,10,Fan increased chance of flourishing.
OL,12,FWhere is the best place to get a good
OL,13,Fview?
OL,15,FClear skies over southern and eastern
OL,16,FEngland will give the clearest view
OL,17,Fearlier in the night - although fog
OL,18,Fpatches developing could obscure the
OL,19,Fview somewhat later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
